title: Innovations Fall/Winter 2016/17: Power to Shine
description: The Innovations Power to Shine theme looks to the brilliance of human ingenuity and creativity with four inspirational design directions: Protectors of Equality (Classic), Saviors of the Planet (Romantic), Explorers of the Future (Progressive) and Guardians of the Past (Glamour). http://www.swarovski.com/professional
